I analyzed data of Nobel Prizes awarded to Women from 1901 to 2019, and built this dashboard using Tableau. Here are some interesting Fact for percentage of Nobel Prizes Awarded to Women (1901-2019) -

1) Between 1901 and 2019, the Nobel Prize have been awarded to 53 women.

2) In year 2009, Nobel Prizes awarded to most women representing 9% of the awards, On the other hand, no woman was awarded in 50s.

3) Peace and Literature are the categories that reward women the most.

4) The nation with the highest number of female Nobel laureates is the United States.
